♪ On the endless cold night ♪

34
00:02:55,410 --> 00:02:57,400
have learned some healing techniques.

35
00:02:57,400 --> 00:03:00,700
♪ Strange is but the crescent moon ♪

36
00:02:59,940 --> 00:03:00,870
There will be...

37
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:03,700
♪ The flute fades far away ♪

38
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:04,070
the next seven years,
and many more after that.

39
00:03:03,950 --> 00:03:07,750
♪ What's familiar will also change ♪

40
00:03:08,010 --> 00:03:10,740
♪ Ice melts in palms ♪

41
