♪ Hope what's hopeful,
and let go of anger in a day ♪

56
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:37,250
I finally discovered that...

57
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:40,220
actually...

58
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:48,430
♪ Yearn for what's yearnable,
live up to it, and never let you go ♪

59
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,810
besides killing...

60
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:46,820
it

61
00:03:48,030 --> 00:03:48,820
might also have

62
00:03:48,820 --> 00:03:49,980
another purpose.

63
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:51,430
♪ Listen to the rain ♪

64
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:54,940
♪ Whispering nonstop in my ears ♪

65
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:52,630
Fang Zhou.

66
00:03:54,220 --> 00:03:55,070
Thank you.

67
